    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah thats fair. but honestly i feel like i can handle it. like if i drink like a ton of water and just cut my dose in half for a couple days to let my stomach settle, that's basically the same as what a doctor would tell me to do to stabilize, right? it seems way safer to just wait it out at home than to go to the ER for just some nausea and shaky hands.",
